# Ignore everything by default
/*

# Log/weights files often found in runs
# If they are too large, you might want to specifically ignore *.pt in runs
# For now, we follow the request to include the folder

# Whitelist allowed files and folders
!/README.md
!/.gitignore
!/base_models/
!/results/
!/runs/
!/scripts/
!/test_image/

# Specifically ignore massive dataset folders
/images/
/labels/
/auto_images/
/implementation_plan.md
/task.md
/walkthrough.md
/git_push_plan.md
/scratch/
/temp/

# Keep the base_models directory even if it has no tracked files (standard git behavior)
!/base_models/**
!/results/**
!/runs/**
!/scripts/**
!/test_image/**
